'''Patricia Altenbernd Johnson''' is a professor of philosophy at [[University of Dayton]]. She has written books about contemporary philosophers. She is a specialist in [[philosophy of religion]], [[hermeneutics]] and 19th and 20th century [[continental philosophy]].
==Works== * "On [[Gadamer]]" ([[Wadsworth Philosophers Series]]), Wadsworth Publishing, 1999. * "On [[Arendt]]" (Wadsworth Philosophers Series), Wadsworth Publishing, 2000. * "On [[Heidegger]]" (Wadsworth Philosophers Series), Wadsworth Publishing, 1999. * "On [[Mary Wollstonecraft|Wollstonecraft]]" (Wadsworth Philosophers Series), Wadsworth Publishing, 1999.
